// Embeds the real brand-mark app icon into growth-layer-agent.exe (see
// build.rs). Windows shows this in Explorer, the taskbar, and the Start
// Menu shortcut/uninstall entry agent.iss already points at the exe's
// own icon resource for (UninstallDisplayIcon={app}\{#MyAppExeName}) --
// so this one resource fixes all of those surfaces at once, not just one.
//
// growth-layer-agent.ico is a byte-for-byte copy of
// installer/windows/assets/growth-layer-agent.ico (both trace back to
// Growth-Layer-Brand-Assets-v1.0/app/windows/growth-layer.ico) --
// duplicated here rather than referenced by a cross-repo relative path
// because RC-compiler path resolution (llvm-rc/windres/rc.exe all
// resolve slightly differently) is exactly the kind of thing not worth
// being clever about for a 608-byte file.
1 ICON "growth-layer-agent.ico"
